sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as SessionProxy
    participant Conn as ServerConnection
    participant Manager as RemoteSessionManager
    participant Session as SessionStub
    participant Service as Underlying service

    Client->>Conn: DeleteSession / transport close
    Conn->>Session: SetConnection(nullptr)
    Conn->>Manager: delete_session_handler(session)
    Manager->>Manager: Remove from session map
    Client-->>Client: Complete pending requests with Bad_Disconnected
    Service-->>Session: Late completion
    Session-->>Session: Ignore, no live connection
